[SN]TITLE[SN]
Body discovered in River Taff near Radyr Weir, Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A body has been found in the River Taff in Cardiff, South Wales Police have said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The discovery was made by canoeists close to Radyr Weir, Radyr, on Saturday shortly after 11:00 BST.
Officers spent about three hours at the scene as part of their investigation.
No further details have been released by police.
